Package: pbfor
Title: Use progress bar with for loops conveniently
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Antoine",
           family = "Fabri",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "antoine.fabri@gmail.com")
Description: 'pbfor' wraps all the features of the package
    'progress'. After the user calls `pb_for(...)`, a regular for loop
    will show a progress bar
